&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Investment team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a rigorous and experienced &lt;strong&gt;Accounting Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to own the accounting function of &lt;strong&gt;Casa de Bolsa Plata&lt;/strong&gt;, a new brokerage firm currently in its pre-operational phase, targeting CNBV licensing in the upcoming months and commencement of operations in December 2026.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role goes beyond day-to-day bookkeeping, you will build the accounting infrastructure of the firm from scratch: chart of accounts, ERP setup, regulatory report templates, and audit frameworks. You will be the financial backbone of the institution and a key participant in the CNBV inspection process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are energized by building something new within a highly regulated environment and you have deep experience in Mexican financial institution accounting, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Challenges that await you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement the firm&#39;s chart of accounts (&lt;strong&gt;catálogo de cuentas&lt;/strong&gt;) in accordance with &lt;strong&gt;CNBV&lt;/strong&gt; standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft the accounting policies and procedures manual&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configure the ERP/accounting system and integrate it with trading and custody platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare the opening balance sheet and capital adequacy analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop &lt;strong&gt;CNBV&lt;/strong&gt; regulatory report templates (R01–R14 as applicable) prior to commencement of live submissions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with external auditors on the annual audit framework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the &lt;strong&gt;CNBV&lt;/strong&gt; commencement-of-operations inspection — financial records section&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Once live: prepare monthly and annual financial statements (&lt;strong&gt;NIF&lt;/strong&gt;-compliant), submit regulatory reports via &lt;strong&gt;SITI&lt;/strong&gt;, and ensure tax compliance before &lt;strong&gt;SAT&lt;/strong&gt; (ISR, IVA, DIOT)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What makes you a great fit:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related field; &lt;strong&gt;Certified Public Accountant (CPC)&lt;/strong&gt; strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 7 years of experience at a regulated financial institution, preferably a &lt;strong&gt;casa de bolsa&lt;/strong&gt; or bank with a brokerage division&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with &lt;strong&gt;CNBV regulatory reports&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;SITI&lt;/strong&gt; submissions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid command of &lt;strong&gt;NIF&lt;/strong&gt; (Normas de Información Financiera) and their application in financial institutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with &lt;strong&gt;SAT&lt;/strong&gt; tax filings in a financial services context (ISR, IVA, DIOT, informative returns)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience building or overhauling accounting systems and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;English conversational level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spanish conversational level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience joining an institution during its pre-operational or start-up phase&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with drafting or reviewing regulatory manuals for CNBV submission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AMIB certification (desirable but not required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience supporting regulatory inspections by the CNBV&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our ways of working:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovative Spirit:&lt;/strong&gt; A commitment to creativity and groundbreaking solutions&lt;/li&gt

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;¡Únete a Banco Plata,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;forma parte de la revolución financiera que inicia su expansión en&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Colombia&lt;/strong&gt;! Acabamos de recibir nuestra licencia bancaria en México y estamos entrando en una etapa de crecimiento, innovación constante y oportunidades reales para quienes quieren construir algo grande!&lt;/p&gt;
