&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Applied Research Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; for the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Risks Team &lt;/strong&gt;to create state of the art foundational deep learning models for fintech. We work with Python, Pytorch, MLFlow, AWS, Snowflake, Claude Code / OpenAI Codex / Cursor.&lt;/p&gt;
