&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a proactive&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Antifraud Analyst Middle &lt;/strong&gt;to strengthen our &lt;strong&gt;Fraud Prevention team&lt;/strong&gt;. This is a role focused on using and developing antifraud rules, analyzing fraud cases, and collaborating closely with agents to improve fraud detection and operational efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
