&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Challenges that await you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your main responsibility will be to test and improve antifraud rules for existing products and new fraud scenarios related to products launching in 2026, balancing security and customer experience&lt;/li&gt;
