&lt;p data-start=&quot;128&quot; data-end=&quot;202&quot;&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;149&quot; data-end=&quot;169&quot;&gt;Business Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to join the &lt;strong&gt;Authentication team&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;The team is responsible for how users securely access and interact with the bank. We build and improve authentication, authorization, and confirmation mechanisms that protect customer accounts while keeping critical user journeys simple and convenient.&lt;/p&gt;
